## Integration Examples

### Generic Chat Application

```python
class ChatLogger:
    """Simple chat logger that can wrap any chat system."""

    def __init__(self, db_path: str = None):
        self.db_path = db_path or str(Path.home() / ".chat_logs" / "messages.db")
        self._init_db()

    def _init_db(self):
