**CLI Version:**
```python
from ace_step import ACEStep

model = ACEStep.from_pretrained("ACE-Step/ACE-Step-v1-3.5B")
audio = model.generate(
    prompt="Upbeat pop song about summer",
    tags=["pop", "upbeat", "summer"],
    duration=180
)
audio.save("summer_song.wav")
```

