Install:

```bash
# Node.js
npm install canvas

# Python
python -m pip install matplotlib
```

Input OHLC format expected by both examples:
- Array of rows: `[timestamp, open, high, low, close]`
- `timestamp` can be unix ms or any x-axis label value

