### query_sqlite_to_csv

Query SQLite database and export to CSV format.

```bash
# Basic query to CSV
sqlite3 database.db <<EOF
.mode csv
.headers on
SELECT * FROM users LIMIT 10;
EOF

# Export to CSV file
sqlite3 database.db <<EOF
.mode csv
.headers on
.output users.csv
SELECT id, name, email, created_at FROM users WHERE active=1;
EOF

